app_name: Groups Control Groups Photo and Video Editing Apps Combine Videos Clip Slideshow
app_description: Combine multiple clips together into one movie with Combine Videos! First add videos from your library. Then take advantage of the simple and easy to use editing features. Crop your video projects just how you want them. Quickly trim out unwanted parts from your video. Add background music from your own music library. Share with your friends on Instagram and YouTube. Your Combine Videos subscription will automatically renew at the end of each term and your credit card will be charged through your iTunes account.
